# QuadRenderSystem  (sbx)

## Purpose
Render bridge for world-space quads: sole adder of DrawQuadInFrameEvent. Each frame it emits one
in-frame draw event per entity that has both a QuadComponent and a resolved WorldTransformComponent,
copying the world matrix and sort key plus the quad's colour and texture id. A null texture id yields
a flat colour quad; a set texture id yields a textured quad. Quads without a world transform yet
(freshly spawned) are skipped until the transform pipeline resolves them.

## Input Components
| Component | Access | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| QuadComponent | read | Colour + texture id |
| WorldTransformComponent | read | World matrix + render sort key |

## Output Components
| Component | Access | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| DrawQuadInFrameEvent | add (inframe) | One per drawable quad; consumed by Renderer2DSystem this frame |
